  "title": "Service Crew",
  "description": "<p>With or without experience welcome. Otherwise, OJT/training will be provided!</p><p></p><p>- Location(s): CBD</p><p>- Working Days: 6 days/week</p><p>- Working Hours: 11am to 11pm (2 hrs break)</p><p></p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p>- Assisting with outlet's co-ordination, preparation and overseeing of the daily operations</p><p>- Engagement in consultative selling</p><p>- Provision of good customer service (attending to guests’ orders, service of food & beverages)</p><p>- Service with a smile, going the extra mile</p><p>- General housekeeping and maintaining of restaurant’s general hygiene</p><p>- Assisting in managing retail sales, merchandising and inventory</p><p>- Preparation and set-up</p><p>- Ad hoc tasks assigned by Supervisor/Management</p><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- Passion for the F&B industry; experienced candidates will be considered for senior positions</p><p>- Service oriented, dynamic and willing to learn</p><p>- Good communication skills</p><p>- Good interpersonal skills</p><p>- Able to work independently and as a team</p><p></p><p>We look forward to working with you!</p>",
